{"tid":994347,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Dyson創辦人138億美元身家躍居英國首富","createTime":"2019-01-24T15:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T15:30:50.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7758d7dd560adc7199c3c020a7edf986b0959082","tid":994347,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190124/640_9d14de454f5bad86e2274f6e781f0fd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190124%2F640_9d14de454f5bad86e2274f6e781f0fd5.jpg&h=0a076a91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拜dyson公司獲利創新高之賜，dyson創辦人、無集塵袋吸塵器之父戴森（James Dyson）已成為英國首富。<br />\n<br />\ndyson周二公布，2018年獲利從2017年的8.01億英鎊升至11億英鎊，反映新護髮產品需求強勁。根據彭博億萬富豪指數，dyson獲利創新高使戴森財富增加約34億美元。目前戴森身價為138億美元（約4263.1億元台幣），擠下化學製品製造商INEOS集團創辦人亨拉特克里夫（Jim Ratcliffe）成為英國首富。<br />\n<br />\n亞洲客群日益壯大已為dyson帶來助益，目前dyson逾半數獲利來自亞洲。阿里巴巴去年11月表示，該公司年度光棍節活動部分熱賣產品來自dyson。<br />\n<br />\ndyson產品以吸塵器和烘手機名聲最響亮，該公司也已進軍空氣清淨機和護髮產品市場，並啟動2021年前開始生產電動車的高成本計劃。dyson執行長羅文（Jim Rowan）表示，dyson計劃把總部從英國英格蘭威爾特郡（Wiltshire）移至新加坡。（林文彬／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190124/1506030/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190124%2F1506030%2F&d=10lau8NziCvWu1GFs4qwqf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=9e4eb58e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190124%2F1506030%2F&h=3dc1ad00\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190124/1506030/</a>"},{"pid":"56e649716f7aa5e55047ce25dcef643181322d40","tid":994347,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oOU0jN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oOU0jN.png&h=4f98e915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想窮都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}